npc <- 30 # nodes per class
Q <- 3 # classes
n <- npc * Q # nodes
Z <- diag(Q) %x% matrix(1, npc,1)
P <- matrix(runif(Q*Q), Q, Q)
A <- 1*(matrix(runif(n*n), n, n )<Z%*%P%*%t(Z))

# estimation
my_model <- BM_bernoulli("SBM", A)
my_model$estimate()
